{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857925018,"sessionID":"ses_286a086e6ffehzsGtZnxuer4fi","part":{"id":"prt_d7960f27a001Bbeotc3mLK2PBC","messageID":"msg_d7960e814001ryHgI3dQMVJNZD","sessionID":"ses_286a086e6ffehzsGtZnxuer4fi","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_f691040dc6be4f29968d27ea","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md","newString":"Key compatibility is maintained across both backends (same key schema, same ZSET semantics).\n\n---\n\n# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-018\n- **Module**: `pkg/agentd`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Status**: Draft\n\n## 1. 概述\n\nAgentd Idle Cleanup Controller 监控 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组的 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` 资源。当资源因长时间无活动而空闲时，控制器自动删除这些资源以释放集群资源。\n\n### 1.1 目标\n\n- 自动清理空闲过期的 AgentRuntime 资源\n- 自动清理空闲过期的 CodeInterpreter 资源\n- 通过 annotation (`agentcube.io/last-activity-time`) 跟踪最后活动时间\n- 支持可配置的空闲超时阈值\n\n### 1.2 依赖\n\n- `github.com/volcano/sh/agentcube/client-go` — Kubernetes typed client\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery` — API 类型定义\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` — Controller 框架\n\n---\n\n## 2. 架构设计\n\n### 2.1 组件结构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      agentd binary                          │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │               controller-runtime Manager               │ │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│ │\n│  │  │         IdleCleanupReconciler                      ││ │\n│  │  │  ┌──────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐     ││ │\n│  │  │  │ AgentRuntime     │  │ CodeInterpreter    │     ││ │\n│  │  │  │ Controller       │  │ Controller         │     ││ │\n│  │  │  └──────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘     ││ │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│ │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 2.2 包结构\n\n```\ncmd/agentd/main.go              # Binary entry point\npkg/agentd/\n├── reconciler.go               # Reconciler 实现\n├── options.go                  # Controller 配置选项\n├── controller.go               # Controller 注册\n└── suite_test.go               # 测试套件\n```\n\n### 2.3 监听资源\n\n| API Group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n|-----------|---------|------|---------|\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `v1alpha1` | `AgentRuntime` | Create/Update/Delete 事件 |\n| `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `v1alpha1` | `CodeInterpreter` | Create/Update/Delete 事件 |\n\n---\n\n## 3. 数据结构\n\n### 3.1 配置常量\n\n```go\npackage agentd\n\nconst (\n    DefaultSessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n    DefaultRequeueDelayOnError      = 30 * time.Second\n    LastActivityAnnotationKey       = \"agentcube.io/last-activity-time\"\n)\n```\n\n### 3.2 Controller 选项\n\n```go\ntype ControllerOptions struct {\n    SessionExpirationTimeout time.Duration\n    MaxConcurrentReconciles  int\n}\n```\n\n默认值：\n- `SessionExpirationTimeout`: 15 分钟\n- `MaxConcurrentReconciles`: 1\n\n### 3.3 Reconciler\n\n```go\ntype Reconciler struct {\n    client.Client\n    Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n    \n    expirationTimeout time.Duration\n}\n\nfunc NewReconciler(c client.Client, s *runtime.Scheme, timeout time.Duration) *Reconciler\nfunc (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)\nfunc (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. API 合约\n\n### 4.1 AgentRuntime\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntimeSpec 包含会话时间配置\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    MaxSessionDuration string `json:\"maxSessionDuration\"` // 例如: \"8h\"\n    SessionTimeout     string `json:\"sessionTimeout\"`     // 例如: \"15m\"\n    TargetPorts        []TargetPort `json:\"targetPorts\"`\n    PodTemplate        *PodTemplateSpec `json:\"podTemplate,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**空闲检测**：控制器读取 `agentcube.io/last-activity-time` annotation。如果存在且超过 `SessionExpirationTimeout`，则删除资源。\n\n### 4.2 CodeInterpreter\n\n```go\n// CodeInterpreterSpec 包含会话时间配置\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    AuthMode             AuthMode `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n    MaxSessionDuration   string   `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n    SessionTimeout       string   `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    Ports                []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    Template             ContainerTemplateSpec `json:\"template\"`\n    WarmPoolSize         int32    `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**空闲检测**：与 AgentRuntime 相同 — 读取 `agentcube.io/last-activity-time` annotation。\n\n---\n\n## 5. 调和逻辑\n\n### 5.1 算法\n\n```\n1. 按 namespace/name 获取资源 (AgentRuntime 或 CodeInterpreter)\n2. 如果 NotFound → 返回 nil error, 不重队列\n3. 如果其他获取错误 → 返回错误, 不重队列\n4. 读取 \"agentcube.io/last-activity-time\" annotation\n5. 如果 annotation 不存在或为空 → 返回 nil, 不重队列\n6. 将 annotation 值解析为 time.RFC3339\n   - 如果解析错误 → 30 秒后重队列并返回错误\n7. 计算 expirationTime = lastActivityTime + SessionExpirationTimeout\n8. 如果 time.Now().After(expirationTime):\n   a. 删除资源\n   b. 如果 NotFound → 返回 nil, 不重队列\n   c. 如果其他删除错误 → 返回错误, 不重队列\n9. 否则 (未过期):\n   a. 计算 requeueAfter = time.Until(expirationTime)\n   b. 返回 RequeueAfter, 无错误\n10. 返回 nil, 不重队列\n```\n\n### 5.2 重队列行为\n\n| 条件 | RequeueAfter | 原因 |\n|------|--------------|------|\n| 解析错误 | 30s | 固定延迟后重试 |\n| 未过期 | `time.Until(expirationTime)` | 等待过期 |\n| 已删除/未找到/无 annotation | 0 | 不重队列 |\n\n---\n\n## 6. 错误处理\n\n### 6.1 删除幂等性\n\n- **删除时 NotFound**: 视为成功，返回 `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n- **其他删除错误**: 返回错误以触发重试\n\n### 6.2 获取 NotFound\n\n- **获取时 NotFound**: 返回 `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` — 资源已被移除\n\n### 6.3 解析错误\n\n- 无效时间戳格式 → 返回 `RequeueAfter: 30s` 和错误\n\n---\n\n## 7. 测试策略\n\n### 7.1 单元测试\n\n1. **ReconcileAgentRuntime**\n   - 测试过期时成功删除\n   - 测试无 annotation 时不删除\n   - 测试未过期时不删除 (验证重队列)\n   - 测试解析错误处理\n   - 测试 Get NotFound 返回 nil\n   - 测试 Delete NotFound 返回 nil\n\n2. **ReconcileCodeInterpreter**\n   - 与 AgentRuntime 相同的测试用例\n\n### 7.2 测试夹具\n\n```go\nfunc TestReconciler_Reconcile(t *testing.T) {\n    tests := []struct {\n        name           string\n        annotation     string\n        expires        bool\n        expectedResult ctrl.Result\n        expectDelete   bool\n        expectError    bool\n    }{\n        {\n            name:           \"expired - should delete\",\n            annotation:     \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n            expires:        true,\n            expectedResult: ctrl.Result{},\n            expectDelete:   true,\n            expectError:    false,\n        },\n        {\n            name:           \"not expired - should requeue\",\n            annotation:     time.Now().Add(-5 * time.Minute).Format(time.RFC3339),\n            expires:        false,\n            expectedResult: ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 10 * time.Minute},\n            expectDelete:   false,\n            expectError:    false,\n        },\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 7.3 集成测试\n\n1. **完整调和循环** — 使用 fake client\n2. **Manager 集成** — 两个 controller 都已注册\n3. **信号处理** — 验证优雅关闭\n\n---\n\n## 8. Manager 配置\n\n```go\nmgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n    Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n    Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n    HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n})\n```\n\n### 8.1 注册 Controller\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntime controller\nerr = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n    For(&runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}).\n    Complete(agentd.NewReconciler(mgr.GetClient(), mgr.GetScheme(), 15*time.Minute))\n\n// CodeInterpreter controller\nerr = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n    For(&runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{}).\n    Complete(agentd.NewReconciler(mgr.GetClient(), mgr.GetScheme(), 15*time.Minute))\n```\n\n---\n\n## 9. 生命周期\n\n### 9.1 启动\n\n1. 解析 flags / 环境变量获取配置\n2. 使用 scheme 构建 controller-runtime manager\n3. 注册两个 controller\n4. 使用 signal handler 启动 manager\n\n### 9.2 关闭\n\n- SIGTERM / SIGINT 触发优雅关闭\n- Manager 停止所有 controller\n- Cache 停止\n- Process 以 exit code 0 退出\n\n---\n\n## 10. 依赖\n\n### 10.1 直接导入\n\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema`\n- `k8s.io/client-go/tools/cache`\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client`\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/controller`\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/manager`\n- `github.com/volcano.sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- `github.com/volcano.sh/agentcube/client-go` (client-go 库)","oldString":"Key compatibility is maintained across both backends (same key schema, same ZSET semantics)."},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":14,"character":1},"end":{"line":14,"character":32}},"severity":1,"code":"UnusedImport","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/internal/typesinternal#UnusedImport"},"source":"compiler","message":"\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/watch\" imported and not used","tags":[1]},{"range":{"start":{"line":65,"character":13},"end":{"line":70,"character":2}},"severity":1,"code":"InvalidIfaceAssign","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/internal/typesinternal#InvalidIfaceAssign"},"source":"compiler","message":"cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)"},{"range":{"start":{"line":80,"character":8},"end":{"line":85,"character":2}},"severity":1,"code":"InvalidIfaceAssign","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tool