{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857928741,"sessionID":"ses_286a086e6ffehzsGtZnxuer4fi","part":{"id":"prt_d796185e6001s5JW1SdWPHp07d","messageID":"msg_d79617bcc001z6xl21s6Mpokn6","sessionID":"ses_286a086e6ffehzsGtZnxuer4fi","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_e9e608a6784b47b1a2aa74ad","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md","offset":1690},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1690: \n1691: Key compatibility is maintained across both backends (same key schema, same ZSET semantics).\n1692: \n1693: ---\n1694: \n1695: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n1696: \n1697: - **AR ID**: AR-018\n1698: - **Module**: `pkg/agentd`\n1699: - **Language**: Go\n1700: - **Size**: S\n1701: - **Status**: Draft\n1702: \n1703: ## 1. 概述\n1704: \n1705: Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller 监控 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组的 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` 资源。当资源因长时间无活动而空闲时，控制器自动删除这些资源以释放集群资源。\n1706: \n1707: ### 1.1 目标\n1708: \n1709: - 自动清理空闲过期的 AgentRuntime 资源\n1710: - 自动清理空闲过期的 CodeInterpreter 资源\n1711: - 通过 annotation (`agentcube.io/last-activity-time`) 跟踪最后活动时间\n1712: - 支持可配置的空闲超时阈值\n1713: \n1714: ### 1.2 依赖\n1715: \n1716: - `github.com/volcano/sh/agentcube/client-go` — Kubernetes typed client\n1717: - `k8s.io/apimachinery` — API 类型定义\n1718: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` — Controller 框架\n1719: \n1720: ---\n1721: \n1722: ## 2. 架构设计\n1723: \n1724: ### 2.1 组件结构\n1725: \n1726: ```\n1727: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n1728: │                      agentd binary                          │\n1729: │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n1730: │  │               controller-runtime Manager               │ │\n1731: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│ │\n1732: │  │  │         IdleCleanupReconciler                      ││ │\n1733: │  │  │  ┌──────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐     ││ │\n1734: │  │  │  │ AgentRuntime     │  │ CodeInterpreter    │     ││ │\n1735: │  │  │  │ Controller       │  │ Controller         │     ││ │\n1736: │  │  │  └──────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘     ││ │\n1737: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│ │\n1738: │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n1739: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n1740: ```\n1741: \n1742: ### 2.2 包结构\n1743: \n1744: ```\n1745: cmd/agentd/main.go              # Binary entry point\n1746: pkg/agentd/\n1747: ├── reconciler.go               # Reconciler 实现\n1748: ├── options.go                  # Controller 配置选项\n1749: ├── controller.go               # Controller 注册\n1750: └── suite_test.go               # 测试套件\n1751: ```\n1752: \n1753: ### 2.3 监听资源\n1754: \n1755: | API Group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n1756: |-----------|---------|------|---------|\n1757: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `v1alpha1` | `AgentRuntime` | Create/Update/Delete 事件 |\n1758: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `v1alpha1` | `CodeInterpreter` | Create/Update/Delete 事件 |\n1759: \n1760: ---\n1761: \n1762: ## 3. 数据结构\n1763: \n1764: ### 3.1 配置常量\n1765: \n1766: ```go\n1767: package agentd\n1768: \n1769: const (\n1770:     DefaultSessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n1771:     DefaultRequeueDelayOnError      = 30 * time.Second\n1772:     LastActivityAnnotationKey       = \"agentcube.io/last-activity-time\"\n1773: )\n1774: ```\n1775: \n1776: ### 3.2 Controller 选项\n1777: \n1778: ```go\n1779: type ControllerOptions struct {\n1780:     SessionExpirationTimeout time.Duration\n1781:     MaxConcurrentReconciles  int\n1782: }\n1783: ```\n1784: \n1785: 默认值：\n1786: - `SessionExpirationTimeout`: 15 分钟\n1787: - `MaxConcurrentReconciles`: 1\n1788: \n1789: ### 3.3 Reconciler\n1790: \n1791: ```go\n1792: type Reconciler struct {\n1793:     client.Client\n1794:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n1795:     \n1796:     expirationTimeout time.Duration\n1797: }\n1798: \n1799: func NewReconciler(c client.Client, s *runtime.Scheme, timeout time.Duration) *Reconciler\n1800: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)\n1801: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error\n1802: ```\n1803: \n1804: ---\n1805: \n1806: ## 4. API 合约\n1807: \n1808: ### 4.1 AgentRuntime\n1809: \n1810: ```go\n1811: // AgentRuntimeSpec 包含会话时间配置\n1812: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n1813:     MaxSessionDuration string `json:\"maxSessionDuration\"` // 例如: \"8h\"\n1814:     SessionTimeout     string `json:\"sessionTimeout\"`     // 例如: \"15m\"\n1815:     TargetPorts        []TargetPort `json:\"targetPorts\"`\n1816:     PodTemplate        *PodTemplateSpec `json:\"podTemplate,omitempty\"`\n1817: }\n1818: ```\n1819: \n1820: **空闲检测**：控制器读取 `agentcube.io/last-activity-time` annotation。如果存在且超过 `SessionExpirationTimeout`，则删除资源。\n1821: \n1822: ### 4.2 CodeInterpreter\n1823: \n1824: ```go\n1825: // CodeInterpreterSpec 包含会话时间配置\n1826: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n1827:     AuthMode             AuthMode `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n1828:     MaxSessionDuration   string   `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n1829:     SessionTimeout       string   `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n1830:     Ports                []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n1831:     Template             ContainerTemplateSpec `json:\"template\"`\n1832:     WarmPoolSize         int32    `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n1833: }\n1834: ```\n1835: \n1836: **空闲检测**：与 AgentRuntime 相同 — 读取 `agentcube.io/last-activity-time` annotation。\n1837: \n1838: ---\n1839: \n1840: ## 5. 调和逻辑\n1841: \n1842: ### 5.1 算法\n1843: \n1844: ```\n1845: 1. 按 namespace/name 获取资源 (AgentRuntime 或 CodeInterpreter)\n1846: 2. 如果 NotFound → 返回 nil error, 不重队列\n1847: 3. 如果其他获取错误 → 返回错误, 不重队列\n1848: 4. 读取 \"agentcube.io/last-activity-time\" annotation\n1849: 5. 如果 annotation 不存在或为空 → 返回 nil, 不重队列\n1850: 6. 将 annotation 值解析为 time.RFC3339\n1851:    - 如果解析错误 → 30 秒后重队列并返回错误\n1852: 7. 计算 expirationTime = lastActivityTime + SessionExpirationTimeout\n1853: 8. 如果 time.Now().After(expirationTime):\n1854:    a. 删除资源\n1855:    b. 如果 NotFound → 返回 nil, 不重队列\n1856:    c. 如果其他删除错误 → 返回错误, 不重队列\n1857: 9. 否则 (未过期):\n1858:    a. 计算 requeueAfter = time.Until(expirationTime)\n1859:    b. 返回 RequeueAfter, 无错误\n1860: 10. 返回 nil, 不重队列\n1861: ```\n1862: \n1863: ### 5.2 重队列行为\n1864: \n1865: | 条件 | RequeueAfter | 原因 |\n1866: |------|--------------|------|\n1867: | 解析错误 | 30s | 固定延迟后重试 |\n1868: | 未过期 | `time.Until(expirationTime)` | 等待过期 |\n1869: | 已删除/未找到/无 annotation | 0 | 不重队列 |\n1870: \n1871: ---\n1872: \n1873: ## 6. 错误处理\n1874: \n1875: ### 6.1 删除幂等性\n1876: \n1877: - **删除时 NotFound**: 视为成功，返回 `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n1878: - **其他删除错误**: 返回错误以触发重试\n1879: \n1880: ### 6.2 获取 NotFound\n1881: \n1882: - **获取时 NotFound**: 返回 `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` — 资源已被移除\n1883: \n1884: ### 6.3 解析错误\n1885: \n1886: - 无效时间戳格式 → 返回 `RequeueAfter: 30s` 和错误\n1887: \n1888: ---\n1889: \n1890: ## 7. 测试策略\n1891: \n1892: ### 7.1 单元测试\n1893: \n1894: 1. **ReconcileAgentRuntime**\n1895:    - 测试过期时成功删除\n1896:    - 测试无 annotation 时不删除\n1897:    - 测试未过期时不删除 (验证重队列)\n1898:    - 测试解析错误处理\n1899:    - 测试 Get NotFound 返回 nil\n1900:    - 测试 Delete NotFound 返回 nil\n1901: \n1902: 2. **ReconcileCodeInterpreter**\n1903:    - 与 AgentRuntime 相同的测试用例\n1904: \n1905: ### 7.2 测试夹具\n1906: \n1907: ```go\n1908: func TestReconciler_Reconcile(t *testing.T) {\n1909:     tests := []struct {\n1910:         name           string\n1911:         annotation     string\n1912:         expires        bool\n1913:         expectedResult ctrl.Result\n1914:         expectDelete   bool\n1915:         expectError    bool\n1916:     }{\n1917:         {\n1918:             name:           \"expired - should delete\",\n1919:             annotation:     \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n1920:             expires:        true,\n1921:             expectedResult: ctrl.Result{},\n1922:             expectDelete:   true,\n1923:             expectError:    false,\n1924:         },\n1925:         {\n1926:             name:           \"not expired - should requeue\",\n1927:             annotation:     time.Now().Add(-5 * time.Minute).Format(time.RFC3339),\n1928:             expires:        false,\n1929:             expectedResult: ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 10 * time.Minute},\n1930:             expectDelete:   false,\n1931:             expectError:    false,\n1932:         },\n1933:     }\n1934: }\n1935: ```\n1936: \n1937: ### 7.3 集成测试\n1938: \n1939: 1. **完整调和循环** — 使用 fake client\n1940: 2. **Manager 集成** — 两个 controller 都已注册\n1941: 3. **信号处理** — 验证优雅关闭\n1942: \n1943: ---\n1944: \n1945: ## 8. Manager 配置\n1946: \n1947: ```go\n1948: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n1949:     Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n1950:     Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n1951:     HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n1952: })\n1953: ```\n1954: \n1955: ### 8.1 注册 Controller\n1956: \n1957: ```go\n1958: // AgentRuntime controller\n1959: err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n1960:     For(&runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}).\n1961:     Complete(agentd.NewReconciler(mgr.GetClient(), mgr.GetScheme(), 15*time.Minute))\n1962: \n1963: // CodeInterpreter controller\n1964: err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n1965:     For(&runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{}).\n1966:     Complete(agentd.NewReconciler(mgr.GetClient(), mgr.GetScheme(), 15*time.Minute))\n1967: ```\n1968: \n1969: ---\n1970: \n1971: ## 9. 生命周期\n1972: \n1973: ### 9.1 启动\n1974: \n1975: 1. 解析 flags / 环境变量获取配置\n1976: 2. 使用 scheme 构建 controller-runtime manager\n1977: 3. 注册两个 controller\n1978: 4. 使用 signal handler 启动 manager\n1979: \n1980: ### 9.2 关闭\n1981: \n1982: - SIGTERM / SIGINT 触发优雅关闭\n1983: - Manager 停止所有 controller\n1984: - Cache 停止\n1985: - Process 以 exit code 0 退出\n1986: \n1987: ---\n1988: \n1989: ## 10. 依赖\n1990: \n1991: ### 10.1 直接导入\n1992: \n1993: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n1994: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n1995: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema`\n1996: - `k8s.io/client-go/tools/cache`\n1997: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`\n1998: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client`\n1999: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/controller`\n2000: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/manager`\n2001: - `github.com/volcano.sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n2002: - `github.com/volcano.sh/agentcube/client-go` (client-go 库)\n\n(End of file - total 2002 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\nKey compatibility is maintained across both backends (same key schema, same ZSET semantics).\n\n---\n\n# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-018\n- **Module**: `pkg/agentd`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Status**: Draft\n\n## 1. 概述\n\nAgentd Idle Cleanup Controller 监控 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组的 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` 资源。当资源因长时间无活动而空闲时，控制器自动删除这些资源以释放集群资源。\n\n### 1.1 目标\n\n- 自动清理空闲过期的 AgentRuntime 资源","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775857928719,"end":1775857928738}}}}
